This product includes software developed independently as a clean-room
TypeScript reimplementation of the public API surface of the Mastra
framework (https://mastra.ai). "Mastra" is referenced nominatively only to
describe the compatible API shape; Redtuma is not affiliated with, endorsed
by, sponsored by, or derived from the Mastra source code or trademarks.

All Redtuma source code, tests, and documentation are authored
independently from public documentation, published type signatures, and
observed runtime behavior. No Mastra source code, comments, test files, or
enterprise-licensed (`ee/`) material has been copied, vendored, or
reimplemented by reading the original implementation. See CLEANROOM.md for
the development process that maintains this separation.

This product builds on the Vercel AI SDK (`ai`) for low-level model and
tool-calling primitives, and uses zod, OpenTelemetry, and Hono.
